## 🔒 Safety & Security

The system is designed with a "Safety Override" protocol. In `geminiService.ts`, safety settings are set to `BLOCK_NONE` to ensure the AI identifies and labels harmful content for the UI rather than crashing the request, allowing the app to provide users with necessary countermeasures and takedown tools.
